|---|---|---|
| No body size limit | DoS via large payloads | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| No security headers | XSS, clickjacking, etc. | `helmet` |
| No rate limiting | Brute force / enumeration | `express-rate-limit` |
| No 404 handler | Info leakage | Custom 404 middleware |
| No error handler | Stack trace exposure / crashes | Global error middleware |
| No input validation | Injection, unexpected behavior | `joi` / `zod` |
| `X-Powered-By` header | Technology fingerprinting | `helmet` or `app.disable(...)` |
| `console.log` for logging | Log injection, poor observability | `pino` / `winston` |

